snippet.title: Ghost of Tsushima -The Ghost | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/ghost-of-tsushima/?emcid=or-1s-412983

Set aside samurai traditions and forge a new path, the path of the Ghost, as you embark on a vast open-world adventure and wage an unconventional war for the freedom of Tsushima. 

Out Summer 2020. 

http://www.ghostoftsushima.com

May contain content inappropriate for children. Visit http://www.esrb.org for rating information.
